            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Balneum Aurelianum ex liberalitate <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli Pii <expan><abbr>Fel</abbr><ex>icis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>servata indulgentia pecuniae eius <lb n="4"/>quam deus Aurelianus concesserat <lb n="5"/>facta usurarum exactione <lb n="6"/>curante Statio Iuliano <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>gregio</ex></expan> curatore <lb n="7"/>res <supplied reason="lost">publica</supplied> refecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist nicht mehr auffindbar. Datierung: je nach Deutung von Z. 2 unter Probus (Sommer 276 - Herbst 282 n. Chr.) oder unter Carus (August / September 282 - Juli / August 283 n. Chr.).</p>
            </div>
